overview: The user aimed to enhance a sleep questionnaire application by adding
  persistent data storage and an administrative interface. The approach involved
  integrating NeonDB with Prisma for the database, developing Next.js API routes
  for data handling, and building a simple admin dashboard. Key decisions
  included using a single password for admin authentication and leveraging
  Next.js middleware for efficient route protection. The implementation
  successfully delivered a functional database, secure admin login, and data
  retrieval/export capabilities, verified through thorough testing.
